ygData.msgSnippet: Dervish are good if you can get a full party I recommend the west commons for the Kodiaks or the dervish camp there.  Its bigger so more loot.  An organised
ygData.messageBody:
Dervish are good if you can get a full party I recommend the west commons
for the Kodiaks or the dervish camp there. Its bigger so more loot. An
organised party can demolish that camp easily.
